scene.message:
Mark: I'm sorry!{nl}
I was right there with her{waitkey}{clearbox}We made it into SEBEC fine,{nl}
but the demons inside{nl}
caught her...{waitkey}{clearbox}They're armed.{nl}
There's no way I can{nl}
take them on alone.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Looks like it's already{nl}
time for me and the{nl}
rest of the gang to shine!{waitkey}{ret}
